-- Create and load DimAirPollution table
CREATE TABLE DimAirPollution (
    aqi INT,
    co FLOAT,
    no FLOAT,
    no2 FLOAT,
    o3 FLOAT,
    so2 FLOAT,
    pm2_5 FLOAT,
    pm10 FLOAT,
    nh3 FLOAT,
    id NVARCHAR(100)
);
GO

INSERT INTO DimAirPollution (
    aqi, 
    co, 
    no, 
    no2, 
    o3, 
    so2, 
    pm2_5, 
    pm10, 
    nh3, 
    id
)
SELECT DISTINCT
    aqi,
    co,
    no,
    no2,
    o3,
    so2,
    pm2_5,
    pm10,
    nh3,
    id
FROM
 ExternalAirPollution;
